uratively, expectancy","kjv_def":"expectation(-ted), hope, live, thing that I long for.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"hope(23x), expectation(7x), line(2x), expected(1x)"},"H8616":{"id":"H8616","lemma":"תִּקְוָה","translit":"Tiqvâh","pron":"tik-vaw'","derivation":"the same as H8615 (תִּקְוָה);","strongs_def":"Tikvah, the name of two Israelites","kjv_def":"Tikvah.","pos":"proper masculine noun","usage":"Tikvah(2x), Tikvath(1x)"},"H8617":{"id":"H8617","lemma":"תְּקוּמָה","translit":"tᵉqûwmâh","pron":"tek-oo-maw'","derivation":"from H6965 (קוּם);","strongs_def":"resistfulness","kjv_def":"power to stand.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"stand(1x)"},"H8618":{"id":"H8618","lemma":"תְּקוֹמֵם","translit":"tᵉqôwmêm","pron":"tek-o-mame'","derivation":"from H6965 (קוּם);","strongs_def":"an opponent","kjv_def":"rise up against."},"H8619":{"id":"H8619","lemma":"תָּקוֹעַ","translit":"tâqôwaʻ","pron":"taw-ko'-ah","derivation":"from H8628 (תָּקַע) (in the musical sense);","strongs_def":"a trumpet","kjv_def":"trumpet.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"trumpet(1x)"},"H8620":{"id":"H8620","lemma":"תְּקוֹעַ","translit":"Tᵉqôwaʻ","pron":"tek-o'-ah","derivation":"a form of H8619 (תָּקוֹעַ);","strongs_def":"Tekoa, a place in Palestine","kjv_def":"Tekoa, Tekoah.","pos":"proper locative noun, proper masculine noun","usage":"Tekoa(6x), Tekoah(1x)"},"H8621":{"id":"H8621","lemma":"תְּקוֹעִי","translit":"Tᵉqôwʻîy","pron":"tek-o-ee'","derivation":"or תְּקֹעִי; patronymically from H8620 (תְּקוֹעַ);","strongs_def":"a Tekoite or inhabitant of Tekoah","kjv_def":"Tekoite.","pos":"gentilic adjective","usage":"Tekoite(5x), Tekoah(2x)"},"H8622":{"id":"H8622","lemma":"תְּקוּפָה","translit":"tᵉqûwphâh","pron":"tek-oo-faw'","derivation":"or תְּקֻפָה; from H5362 (נָקַף);","strongs_def":"a revolution, i.e. (of the sun) course, (of time) lapse","kjv_def":"circuit, come about, end.","pos":"feminine noun","usage":"end(2x), circuit(1x)"},"H8623":{"id":"H8623","lemma":"תַּקִּיף","translit":"taqqîyph","pron":"tak-k